dc_title_s: Silesiae ducatus: nova et accurata descriptio.
dc_description_s: Relief shown pictorially. Includes German coat of arms above the title cartouche. From "Atlantis Maioris Appendix", Johannes Janssonius, 1630. 1 map; 37 x 49 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
